**Formula:**
```javascript
S-ROI = sin(timestamp × 0.0043) + 1.618
S-ROI = sin((timestamp_ms / 1000) × 0.0043) + 1.618
```
Where `timestamp_ms` is converted from milliseconds to seconds before applying the 0.0043 Hz resonance frequency.
